html.md
# HTML

HTML is used to create the structure of a webpage.
HTML uses tags like <html>, <head>, and <body>.
## HTML File Structure

HTML files contain elements wrapped inside tags.
## What HTML Does

HTML defines the structure of a webpage using elements and tags.
## Simple HTML Example

```html
<h1>Hello World</h1>
<p>This is a paragraph</p>
## Common HTML Tags

- `<h1>` for headings  
- `<p>` for paragraphs  
- `<a>` for links  
## HTML Comments

Comments are notes that do not appear on the webpage.
## HTML Comment Example

```html
<!-- This is a comment -->
## HTML Attributes

Attributes provide extra information about elements.
## HTML Lists

HTML supports ordered and unordered lists.
## HTML List Example

```html
<ul>
  <li>Item 1</li>
  <li>Item 2</li>
</ul>
